1:1 o presbuterov gaiw tw agaphtw, on egw agapw en alhyeia.

1:2 agaphte, peri pantwn eucomai se euodousyai kai ugiainein,
 kaywv euodoutai sou h quch.
1:3 ecarhn gar lian ercomenwn adelfwn kai marturountwn sou
 th alhyeia, kaywv su en alhyeia peripateiv.
1:4 meizoteran toutwn ouk ecw caran, ina akouw ta ema tekna
 en alhyeia peripatounta.

1:5 agaphte, piston poieiv o ean ergash eiv touv adelfouv
 kai eiv touv xenouv,
1:6 oi emarturhsan sou th agaph enwpion ekklhsiav, ouv kalwv
 poihseiv propemqav axiwv tou yeou.
1:7 uper gar tou onomatov exhlyon, mhden lambanontev apo twn
 eynikwn.
1:8 hmeiv oun ofeilomen apolambanein touv toioutouv, ina sunergoi
 ginwmeya th alhyeia.
1:9 egraqa th ekklhsia: all o filoprwteuwn autwn diotrefhv
 ouk epidecetai hmav.
1:10 dia touto, ean elyw, upomnhsw autou ta erga a poiei,
 logoiv ponhroiv fluarwn hmav: kai mh arkoumenov epi toutoiv
 oute autov epidecetai touv adelfouv kai touv boulomenouv
 kwluei kai [ek] thv ekklhsiav ekballei.
1:11 agaphte, mh mimou to kakon, alla to agayon. o agayopoiwn
 ek tou yeou estin: o kakopoiwn ouc ewraken ton yeon.
1:12 dhmhtriw memarturhtai upo pantwn kai up authv thv alhyeiav:
 kai hmeiv de marturoumen, kai oidate oti h marturia hmwn
 alhyhv estin.

1:13 polla eicon grafein, all ou yelw dia melanov kai kalamou
 soi graqai:
1:14 elpizw de euyewv idein se, kai stoma prov stoma lalhsomen. eirhnh 
 soi. aspazontai se oi filoi. aspazou touv filouv kat onoma.
